      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Sonoma Coast, California</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A strong Sonoma bottle for understanding why the region feels fresher and more site-driven than the standard Napa picture. It is not about power first.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Pinot Noir</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-100">
