      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Napa Valley, California</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A useful Napa reference because it shows concentration and prestige without turning cartoonishly ripe. This is the style many buyers mean when they say they want Napa.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Cabernet Sauvignon</p>
    </div>
